      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 27.6 - 老子 27.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 27.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是以聖人常善救人，故無棄人；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the same way the sage is always skilful at saving men, and so he does not cast away any man;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
