      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 27.15 - 老子 27.17</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 27.11</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不貴其師，不愛其資，雖智大迷，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If the one did not honour his master, and the other did not rejoice in his helper, an (observer), though intelligent, might greatly err about them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
